## ğŸ“Š Key Findings

* âœ… **Customer Experience & Quality:** Stable ratings and a **0% return rate** indicate high customer satisfaction.
* ğŸ’¸ **Discount Strategy:** Outerwear has **lower discount penetration** than other departments, limiting sales volume.
