## ğŸ§  Conclusion

The underperformance of the outerwear department is **not** caused by poor customer experience or low perceived value. Instead, it is primarily driven by **strong seasonality**, **conservative discounting**, and **limited bundle-based promotions**. Optimizing these areas presents a clear opportunity to improve revenue while maintaining sustainable profitability.

